name: Paulie on the roof
description:
Paulie, Paulie stop playing on the roof, 
Your band playing make the neighbour shove
The old lady got annoyed and sent bobbies to the roof
The bobbies come and look for the proof

Celebrating the release of the new Bee-less documentary series.

This NFT is part 1 of 4 collectible NFT of the boys playing on the rooftop

Collect four of them and get a free exclusive secret NFT, happy collecting! (limited time only)
